You know. it's... It's jubilant.

139
00:08:32.174 --> 00:08:33.424
- Jubilant.
- Yeah.

140
00:08:33.564 --> 00:08:35.144
Show me the orange one. bigger.

141
00:08:36.454 --> 00:08:38.634
Okay. bossy.

142
