171
00:10:32.364 --> 00:10:33.364
Amanda.

172
00:10:33.474 --> 00:10:34.474
Should you be here?

173
00:10:34.544 --> 00:10:35.754
Probably not.

174
00:10:36.374 --> 00:10:39.094
