177
00:10:44.104 --> 00:10:46.584
Yes. I did. You're too close to this. will.

178
00:10:46.724 --> 00:10:49.524
Okay. Well then. I guess. you
know. I'll just go take a bubble bath

179
00:10:49.664 --> 00:10:51.555
